EmailTemplate.textOnly:
Lead Converted to Opportunity: {!Opportunity.Name}

Hello {!Opportunity.Owner.FirstName},

A lead has been successfully converted to an opportunity and assigned to you. Please follow up with the customer to discuss next steps.

Opportunity Details:
- Name: {!Opportunity.Name}
- Account: {!Opportunity.Account}
- Amount: {!Opportunity.Amount}
- Close Date: {!Opportunity.CloseDate}
- Region: {!Opportunity.Region__c}

A follow-up task has been created and assigned to you. Please review it in your task list.

Best regards,
Sales Operations Team
